game.name: Vincy Cooking Rainbow Birthday Cake
game.description:
Vincy has planned to celebrate her birthday tomorrow. She loves preparing some unique recipe on her own on his every birthday. Today she has decided to prepare a rainbow cake to surprise all her guests during this year birthday party. She has got this idea from the internet and the good news is that she has downloaded the complete recipe online. Would you help her to guide how to follow the recipe and prepare a delicious rainbow cake? Join Vincy Cooking Rainbow Birthday Cake and be prepared to create an awesome birthday cake of this lovely girl!

The problem is that she does not have enough time to waste. So try to be quick in preparing this awesome cake recipe and bringing some color into your life. Start by mixing all the ingredients and then playing with some food coloring! Get ready to use the oven to bake your cakes and then decorate them with the help of some yummy sweets in this HTML5 cooking game! Make sure to blend your useful ingredients and then separate it into multiple pans.

It is up to you which color you want to give your cakes! Do not forget to layer your colored cakes on top of each other. You would also spot the needful icing to make it delicious. There are different types of beautiful butterflies that you can use to make your cake good-looking and stand out from others. Once you are done, cut your cake into a plate and then get ready to see its lovely rainbow colors before having it. Give our other tricky cake decoration games and have fun alone or with your friends, no download required!
